reviews.headline: Love this product!
reviews.comments: This is the best moisurizer, I love the smell and the way it makes my skin look.

reviews.headline: does nothing and causes acne
reviews.comments: I'm a massive EL fan but I really hate this eye cream. It smells wicked good and feels SOOOO nice but it doesn't do jack. It's made me consistently break out in the facial skin area below my eyes (aka the dark circles I'm futilely trying to exorcize).

reviews.headline: Not great
reviews.comments: I'm not sure how this product has so many good reviews I guess I must be one of the people it just did not work for. I bought it when it was on sale. I could not imagine paying full price for it. I am 35 with a little bit of puffiness and dark circles from being a tired working mom. After two months of using this, I still have puffiness and dark circles. Nothing's changed. I do not feel like cooling sensation either. And if your eyes water while it's on and it gets in your eye at all it burns - it does not absorb very well. I wouldn't ever buy this again.

reviews.headline: Say goodbye to the dark circles under your eyes!
reviews.comments: This stuff will brighten the dark circles under your eyes QUICK! I will never go without this stuff!

reviews.headline: Soothes dryness
reviews.comments: I initially purchased this when I was having a reaction to a product drying out my under eye, and it helped so much! I don't necessarily feel like it reduces the creases/fine lines, but it is definitely very cooling and soothing!

reviews.headline: I Use This Every Day
reviews.comments: This is a wonderful product. It's lightweight and blends smoothly into the area round my eyes. Makes the skin look and feel great.

reviews.headline: Nothing like this eye gel!
reviews.comments: The best, hands down, eye treatment for daily wear. Wouldn't be without it.

reviews.headline: A Must Have
reviews.comments: I love this product. Actually received in a gift with purchase. Now I cannot do without it. Makes my eyes & the skin around my eyes youthful and wrinkle free.

reviews.headline: Great product!
reviews.comments: I love this product. It is very moisturizing. It doesn't burn my eyes like some products.

reviews.headline: Estee Lauder Rocks Moms favorite brand and mine too.
reviews.comments: Best eye cream ever.

reviews.headline: Turned my skin yellow
reviews.comments: It was moisturizing however I have an olive undertone I am half native American so not super pale but not super tan I usually wear like a medium sand color, but this literally was turning my circles yellow. I am not trying to look like I have jaundice, so will be returning. Probably works better for lighter skin.

reviews.headline: Not sure
reviews.comments: I was really excited to try this out but about 2 days of using it, it caused some sort of reaction to my undereye and top of cheeks. It became severely dry where my makeup would look flaky. I plan on returning the product.

reviews.headline: Very refreshing under eyes
reviews.comments: To soothe tired eyes

reviews.headline: A must have for skincare routine
reviews.comments: I got it on sale and i regret i didn't buy a few because it's so good! Now i have to repurchase full price! It doesn't have fragrance and give your eye area a cool comfortable feeling! Love it!

reviews.headline: Love the cooling sensation
reviews.comments: For a women in her late forties moisture is key, and this falls a little short of moisturizing like I need it to. I love the cooling sensation, makes my eyes feel awake. I got this at half price so for what I paid for it I would say over all not a bad product.

reviews.headline: Nice eye creme
reviews.comments: Have not used long enough to comment on efficacy of wrinkle reduction, but it does moisturize and reduce puffiness. I have severely dry under eye area and this does help. I am still in search of one that moisturizes more and lasts throughout the day, but this definitely helps and feels great on. Would be wonderful for those with moderate to dry under eye area.

reviews.headline: Best eye cream ever!!
reviews.comments: I apply every morning on my both of my eye areas! It feels so cool and refreshing! It makes my skin feel so smooth and hydrated!!

reviews.headline: I love this eye cream
reviews.comments: I'm loving this eye cream. I'm in my 30s and it really seems to be helping with my fine lines and keeping them hydrated. It doesn't really have a smell and it absorbs nicely without being greasy. I use it morning and night. I would recommend this product for anyone wanting help with those issues.

reviews.headline: DARK CIRCLES GONE@
reviews.comments: I've tried several products to help with my dark circles and have been unsuccessful up until now. It's been 2 weeks and I've seen a significant difference already!

reviews.headline: AMAZING!!
reviews.comments: I've tried SO many products for dark circles and puffiness. This one wins the ultimate prize!!! I love it!  My search is finally over.

faceoff_positive.comments: I received an email introducing this product. I bought it, and YES it really depuffs the bags under your eyes!! I've been trying all sorts of eye products for years without results. When I woke up this morning after only one application I LOVED what my eyes looked like. I can only image what the effects will be after using this product for a while. I am so excited and relieved to finally find something that works for me.
faceoff_positive.headline: Fantastic Eye Cream That Works!

faceoff_negative.comments: I purchased Day Wear Eye Cream hoping it would help with the under eye area. So far it has been disappointing. I have seen no improvement at all. I must say I'm a little disappointed with the results. I will continue to use it hoping with prolong use it will bring better results.
